be willing to receiue their pay in ſuch crackt coine:) but
ſinne dealeth ſo with vs; when we haue yeelded all the
powers and faculties of our-ſoules, and the members of
our bodies, to be commanded by ſinne, whats the reward
he giues vs but death? ſo ſaith the Apoſtle in the
laſt verſe of this Chapter:Rom. 6. v. vlt. 
